data.value:
Hello! This tool was written to fill the need for a suitable 2D map editor for Mojang's Minecraft. As I am a third party I claim no ownership over Mojang, Minecraft, or any other of Mojang's property. This program makes use of the Substrate library developed by Justin Aquadro, please visit http://code.google.com/p/substrate-minecraft for details. This product has been distributed free of charge (should you have paid for it please demand your money be returned to you). Also, should you find a bug in the program: 1: Reproduce the bug, so that you know how it happened. 2: Report the bug in as much detail as possible (so that I know how to reproduce it and subsequently fix it) to bug.report.creativemodeplus@gmail.com
